# =============================================================================
# FliVideo Shared Configuration Repository
# =============================================================================
#
# PURPOSE:
# This is a minimal git repo that ONLY tracks shared Claude Code configuration
# (commands and skills) used across all FliVideo projects.
#
# WHY THIS EXISTS:
# - FliVideo is NOT a monorepo - each subproject (flihub, flideck, etc.) has
#   its own independent git repository
# - We wanted shared /po, /dev, /uat commands that all projects inherit
# - Claude Code looks up the directory tree for .claude/ folders, so placing
#   shared config here makes it available to all child projects
# - Without this repo, the .claude/ files would be untracked and at risk
#
# STRUCTURE:
# /Users/davidcruwys/dev/ad/flivideo/
# ├── .git/                    ← This repo (tracks only .claude/)
# ├── .gitignore               ← This file
# ├── .claude/                 ← TRACKED - shared commands & skills
# │   ├── commands/            ← /po, /dev, /uat, /progress, /brainstorming-agent
# │   └── skills/              ← handover-queue, po-templates
# ├── flihub/                  ← IGNORED - separate git repo
# ├── flideck/                 ← IGNORED - separate git repo
# └── [other projects]/        ← IGNORED - separate git repos
#
# HOW INHERITANCE WORKS:
# When you run Claude Code in /flivideo/flideck/, it finds:
#   1. /flivideo/flideck/.claude/     (project-specific overrides)
#   2. /flivideo/.claude/             (shared commands - THIS REPO)
#   3. ~/.claude/                     (user-level config)
#
# =============================================================================

# Ignore everything by default
*

# Except this file
!.gitignore

# And the shared Claude configuration
!.claude/
!.claude/**
